        <div class="hero">
            <div class="hero-sec">
                <div class="hero-content">
                    <h1><span>UNDERSTAND</span> VIDEOS & PDF EASILY WITH THE HELP OF AI</h1>
                    <p>Get the most out of videos, YouTube or those boring lectures that you would normally never
